dreisoft.tresos.tresosdb.api.model.v2.commonstructure.constants

Interface IConstantSpecificationMapping

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IEntity

    public interface IConstantSpecificationMapping
extends IEntity
    IConstantSpecificationMapping: Entity class of the tresosDB model.

    This meta-class is used to create an association of two ConstantSpecifications. One ConstantSpecification is supposed to be defined in the application domain while the other should be defined in the implementation domain. Hence the ConstantSpecificationMapping needs to be used where a ConstantSpecification defined in one domain needs to be associated to a ConstantSpecification in the other domain. This information is crucial for the RTE generator.
